'''哈奇森效應'''（{{lang-en|'''Hutchison Effect'''}}），又名'''H效应'''或'''零重力效应'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://xhmgs-6464.blog.163.com/blog/static/1688273520114302196170/ |title=H效应（The Hutchison Effect / 零重力效应）的详细介绍 |date=2011-05-30 |accessdate=2013-07-12 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208064524/http://xhmgs-6464.blog.163.com/blog/static/1688273520114302196170/ |archivedate=2015-12-08 }}</ref>，是[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]的一系列[[偽科學|偽科學]]現象，相傳於1979年由[[加拿大|加拿大]]科學家[[約翰·哈奇森|約翰·哈奇森]]所發現，透過操縱[[電磁場|電磁場]]可以得到[[反重力|反重力]]的現象<ref>{{cite video
 |people      = John Hutchison (creator)
 |date        = 2003
 |title       = Video clip of a "levitating" toy UFO
 |url         = http://www.uforc.com/Video_2.WMV
 |format      = [[WMV|WMV]]
 |accessdate  = 2006-12-10
 |medium      = [http://www.uforc.com/antigravity/blackops.html News release]
 |publisher   = [http://www.uforc.com UFO Research Center]
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20070208022028/http://www.uforc.com/Video_2.WMV
 |archivedate = 2007-02-08
}} {{Wayback|url=http://www.uforc.com/Video_2.WMV |date=20070208022028 }}</ref>，或者會令兩種不相關的物質（例如：金屬與木頭，人與機器）融合在一起<ref>{{cite web 
 |url=http://www.geocities.com/ResearchTriangle/Thinktank/8863/jkh_efct.html 
 |title=The Hutchison Effect – An Explanation 
 |accessdate=2006-12-10 
 |last=Solis 
